# IFRS Statement Generator — Commercial Grade Architecture
## "Map Once, Use Forever" Pattern (BlackLine-style)

## CORE CONCEPT

The IFRS Statement Generator uses a **mapping persistence pattern**:
1. **First time**: Company uploads Chart of Accounts → GL codes mapped to IFRS line items → Saved forever
2. **Every month after**: Upload Trial Balance → 100% auto-mapped using saved mappings (0 manual work)
3. **New GL codes**: Only map the new code → Add to saved mappings
4. **Result**: 60-second statement generation from raw Trial Balance

AI Provider: **AWS Bedrock Amazon Nova Lite** (swappable to Claude/OpenAI via config)

