## PHASE 3: MAPPING SERVICE (src/services/mappingService.ts)

### IFRS Master Line Items (Standard Reference)
Contains ~30 standard IFRS line items across:
- Balance Sheet Assets (current + non-current)
- Balance Sheet Liabilities (current + non-current)
- Balance Sheet Equity
- P&L line items (revenue, COGS, opex categories, finance, tax)

Format: `{ value: "financialPosition.assets.current.cashAndEquivalents", label: "Cash & Cash Equivalents", statement: "balanceSheet" }`

### Storage Functions
```typescript
// localStorage implementation (replace with Supabase in production)
saveCompanyMappings(companyId, mappings)    // Save to persistent storage
loadCompanyMappings(companyId)              // Load saved mappings
hasCompanyMappings(companyId)               // Check if company is set up
```

### Auto-Mapping Logic
```typescript
autoMapTrialBalance(trialBalance, companyId)
// Returns: { mapped: entries[], newCodes: entries[], mappedCount: number }
// - Mapped: GL codes found in saved mappings
// - New Codes: GL codes added since last upload (need mapping)
```

### AI Suggestion Logic
```typescript
getAISuggestions(entries)
// Calls AI to suggest IFRS mappings for unmapped/new GL codes
// Returns: { "5004": "profitLoss.operatingExpenses.administrative", ... }
```

